* List of Batman family enemies
* Algol – The name Algol derives from the Arabic رأس الغول ra&#x27;s al-ghūl. The English name &quot;Demon&#x27;s Head&quot; is a direct translation of this, as Ra&#x27;s is head, Ghoul is Demon.
* Eurasian nomads
* Alexander the Great
* Fu Manchu
* Secret society
